  13 Apr 2006; Diego Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  mesa-progs-6.4.2.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  11 Apr 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  mesa-progs-6.4.2.ebuild, mesa-progs-6.5.ebuild:
  Set DEPEND equal to RDEPEND, not equal to itself, which was empty, causing
  build issues. Reported by Ciaran McCreesh.

*mesa-progs-6.5 (01 Apr 2006)

  01 Apr 2006; Joshua Baergen <joshuabaergen@gentoo.org>
  +mesa-progs-6.5.ebuild:
  Add the 6.5 versions of the Mesa demo applications.

  05 Mar 2006; Stefaan De Roeck <stefaan@gentoo.org>
  mesa-progs-6.4.2.ebuild:
  Marked ~alpha (bug #122726)

*mesa-progs-6.4.2 (14 Feb 2006)

  14 Feb 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  -mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild, +mesa-progs-6.4.2.ebuild:
  (#122851) Die on errors, reported by Christophe <cjouny@gmail.com>. Also
  update to 6.4.2 tarball to reduce downloads.

  14 Feb 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64

  31 Jan 2006; Rene Nussbaumer <killerfox@gentoo.org>
  mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Unstable on hppa.

  16 Dec 2005; Herbie Hopkins <herbs@gentoo.org> mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Explicitly unset PIC_FLAGS else -fPIC gets used on amd64 anyway.

  15 Dec 2005; Stephen P. Becker <geoman@gentoo.org>
  mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  added ~mips keyword

  14 Dec 2005; Herbie Hopkins <herbs@gentoo.org> mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64 wrt bug #115539.

  14 Dec 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  (#115539) Remove PIC flags, because they should only be used on the
  libraries, not the apps.

  14 Dec 2005; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Adding ~ppc. Added RDEPEND as well.

  14 Dec 2005; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org> mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc keyword --- Bug 115539.

*mesa-progs-6.4.1 (14 Dec 2005)

  14 Dec 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; +metadata.xml,
  +mesa-progs-6.4.1.ebuild:
  This provides glxgears and glxinfo. In the future, it may be enhanced to
